50fec41","tid":16879,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仆街係咪要轉去花旗開戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支爆<br />\n但支那揸住咁多美國債券會唔會拖埋美帝落水？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美帝總統有權唔比債券拋售，即係可以唔認數，當然唔係打杖時都唔會咁做啦"},{"pid":"dc6e1474f4129f3e63b9889dca7529bd3615501c","tid":16879,"uid":35461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://tw.aboluowang.com/2016/1201/843575.html?utm_campaign=shareaholic&amp;amp;utm_medium=facebook&amp;amp;utm_source=socialnetwork\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.aboluowang.com%2F2016%2F1201%2F843575.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dshareaholic%26amp%3Butm_medium%3Dfacebook%26amp%3Butm_source%3Dsocialnetwork&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8IscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=26a828f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.aboluowang.com/2016/1201/843575.html?utm_campaign=shareaholic&amp;amp;utm_medium=facebook&amp;amp;utm_source=socialnetwork</a><br />\n<br />\n英格蘭銀行將於當地時間周三下午公布對7家最大銀行進行的史上最嚴格壓力測試結果，分析師指出，若中國經濟衰退和香港房市崩盤，對中國和香港曝險最多的滙豐銀行和渣打銀行很可能面臨倒閉風險。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭銀行已對巴克萊銀行、蘇格蘭皇家銀行、滙豐銀行、渣打銀行、駿懋銀行（Lloyds Banking）、西班牙國際銀行（Banco Santander）英國分行、英國房屋抵押貸款協會（Nationwide）等7銀行進行3輪壓力測試，希望迫使銀行業改善資本緩衝，以避免未來發生金融危機時倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n對中、港曝險最多<br />\n<br />\nAutonomous Research分析師認為，巴克萊銀行和蘇格蘭皇家銀行將無法通過測試，對2家銀行將是一大打擊。不過，由於這次測試是依據7家銀行去年底的財務狀況進行，2家銀行自此之後已提高資本，英格蘭銀行可能不會對2家銀行採取監管行動。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭銀行進行的第1輪壓力測試，模擬英國房價崩盤，第2輪測試模擬中國經濟<span style=\"color: red;\">硬著陸</span>，第3輪測試則模擬英國衰退，香港房市崩盤，中國、歐元區和美國萎縮，所引發的全球經濟風暴。<br />\n<br />\nAutonomous分析師指出，由於巴克萊銀行在美國布局甚深，可能因為美國衰退而受創。此外，蘇格蘭皇家銀行因為仍有不少罰款和訴訟得面對，一旦發生上述情況，也恐難逃一劫。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大皇家銀行資本市場（RBC Capital Markets）分析師則指出，中國經濟萎縮和香港房市崩盤，對聚焦於亞洲市場的滙豐銀行和渣打銀行將構成最大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大皇家銀行分析師諾伯表示，滙豐銀行和渣打銀行也有可能無法通過壓力測試，因為英格蘭銀行可能提高2家銀行在中國或與中國有關的曝險損失。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a83709af79baf9a244ae4a64ce47b57a6dbdec","tid":16879,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"692d97ffca557f8f9d64a220ad223f28aa51f5d2","tid":16879,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"一早係花旗用戶"},{"pid":"d2903a91025ebf8cdaf2bfdb42a57fb61e133845","tid":16879,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"個模擬玩到咁大，我反而想知咩銀行會唔死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359f4fbe618f7951ef10f87fcd022f4f4ccf21c9","tid":16879,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"大前提要支爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251616dd15288281ae9772ef16269d8bfb93b1d0","tid":16879,"uid":23235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"一早轉左用citibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n型過用hsbc中銀幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40936f5ba68252512d5c18bd1d4d9e6bd093b37c","tid":16879,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個模擬玩到咁大，我反而想知咩銀行會唔死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係講緊中英崩盤 其實其他國家因素冇計戊去就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6531e5f150597966ff70348117f1f4fac49e253","tid":16879,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早轉左用citibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n型過用hsbc中銀幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係出事時會有用咩"},{"pid":"51112705ce51fccccfa7f6031b158bd80f9ee5b7","tid":16879,"ui